title: Apple's Weather App Isn't Working on iPhones
description: Service may be slow or unavailable, the tech company said. It hasn’t given a reason for the outage.

title: TikTok Fined by U.K. Regulator for Misuse of Children's Data
description: U.K. authorities fined TikTok $15.8 million for breaching the country’s data-protection laws.

title: Australia Bans TikTok From Government Devices Amid Security Concerns
description: With the decision, Australia joins the U.S. and all other members of the so-called Five Eyes intelligence alliance in restricting government access to the video-sharing app
